        <release version="1.4.0" date="2025-04-30">
            <description>
                <p>No longer set the wallpaper automatically while the main window is visible, to allow you to preview different sources without actually changing your desktop background.</p>
                <p>No longer attempt to set the wallpaper automatically while the session is locked, or the system is on low power or has no network connection.</p>
                <p>Notify and ask to restart app when it was updated in the background.</p>
            </description>
            <issues>
